Package: surveymapR
Type: Package
Title: Create Maps Around Survey Transects or Points
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Georg Andersson
Maintainer: Georg Andersson <georg.andersson@biol.lu.se>
Description: This package create maps that show overview and specifics of transects and points in a survey.
    This can then be used in field to get to the specific site and then orient one self to where the surveys should be.
